            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThe%20Word%20of%20God%20is%20the%20one%20factor%20in%20your%20life%20that%20will%20determine%20your%20level%20of%20blessing.%20David%20wrote%20that%20the%20person%20whose%20delight%20is%20in%20the%20law%20of%20the%20Lord%20would%20find%20that%20whatever%20he%20does%20prospers%20(Psalm%201%3A2-3).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJosiah's%20life%20turned%20completely%20around%20the%20moment%20the%20high%20priest%20said%20he%20had%20located%20the%20Book%20of%20the%20Law%20in%20the%20temple%20of%20the%20Lord.%20Reading%20the%20Word%20sparked%20a%20righteous%20indignation%20in%20Josiah's%20spirit%2C%20and%20he%20cleansed%20both%20Judah%20and%20Israel%20of%20their%20false%20gods%20with%20a%20determination%20unsurpassed%20in%20biblical%20history.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EYour%20heart%20may%20be%20predisposed%20to%20serving%20God%2C%20but%20hearing%20the%20Word%20in%20your%20heart%20will%20light%20the%20fire%20of%20conviction.%20If%20you%20devote%20your%20life%20to%20reading%20and%20meditating%20on%20the%20Word%2C%20you%20will%20remain%20continually%20opposed%20to%20sin.%20You%20will%20also%20be%20disposed%20to%20God%20and%20to%20fulfilling%20the%20destiny%20He%20has%20for%20you.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20this%20second%20half%20of%20the%20year%2C%20devote%20yourself%20fully%20to%20the%20Word%20of%20God.%20Read%20and%20devour%20it%20as%20would%20a%20hungry%20person%2C%20and%20put%20whatever%20you%20read%20into%20practice.%20When%20you%20do%2C%20the%20Lord%20promises%20that%20you%20will%20be%20blessed!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "2Kgs.22:3-23:30",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Kings%2022%3A3-23%3A30%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20the%20eighteenth%20year%20of%20his%20reign%2C%20King%20Josiah%20sent%20Shaphan%20son%20of%20Azaliah%20and%20grandson%20of%20Meshullam%2C%20the%20court%20secretary%2C%20to%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20He%20told%20him%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20to%20Hilkiah%20the%20high%20priest%20and%20have%20him%20count%20the%20money%20the%20gatekeepers%20have%20collected%20from%20the%20people%20at%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EEntrust%20this%20money%20to%20the%20men%20assigned%20to%20supervise%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple.%20Then%20they%20can%20use%20it%20to%20pay%20workers%20to%20repair%20the%20Temple.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20will%20need%20to%20hire%20carpenters%2C%20builders%2C%20and%20masons.%20Also%20have%20them%20buy%20the%20timber%20and%20the%20finished%20stone%20needed%20to%20repair%20the%20Temple.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20require%20the%20construction%20supervisors%20to%20keep%20account%20of%20the%20money%20they%20receive%2C%20for%20they%20are%20honest%20and%20trustworthy%20men.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EHilkiah%20Discovers%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Law%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EHilkiah%20the%20high%20priest%20said%20to%20Shaphan%20the%20court%20secretary%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20found%20the%20Book%20of%20the%20Law%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple!%26%23x201D%3B%20Then%20Hilkiah%20gave%20the%20scroll%20to%20Shaphan%2C%20and%20he%20read%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EShaphan%20went%20to%20the%20king%20and%20reported%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYour%20officials%20have%20turned%20over%20the%20money%20collected%20at%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20the%20workers%20and%20supervisors%20at%20the%20Temple.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EShaphan%20also%20told%20the%20king%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHilkiah%20the%20priest%20has%20given%20me%20a%20scroll.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20Shaphan%20read%20it%20to%20the%20king.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20king%20heard%20what%20was%20written%20in%20the%20Book%20of%20the%20Law%2C%20he%20tore%20his%20clothes%20in%20despair.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20gave%20these%20orders%20to%20Hilkiah%20the%20priest%2C%20Ahikam%20son%20of%20Shaphan%2C%20Acbor%20son%20of%20Micaiah%2C%20Shaphan%20the%20court%20secretary%2C%20and%20Asaiah%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20personal%20adviser%3A%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20to%20the%20Temple%20and%20speak%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20me%20and%20for%20the%20people%20and%20for%20all%20Judah.%20Inquire%20about%20the%20words%20written%20in%20this%20scroll%20that%20has%20been%20found.%20For%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20great%20anger%20is%20burning%20against%20us%20because%20our%20ancestors%20have%20not%20obeyed%20the%20words%20in%20this%20scroll.%20We%20have%20not%20been%20doing%20everything%20it%20says%20we%20must%20do.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Hilkiah%20the%20priest%2C%20Ahikam%2C%20Acbor%2C%20Shaphan%2C%20and%20Asaiah%20went%20to%20the%20New%20Quarter%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E22%3A14%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Second%20Quarter%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20newer%20section%20of%20Jerusalem.%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Mishneh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Jerusalem%20to%20consult%20with%20the%20prophet%20Huldah.%20She%20was%20the%20wife%20of%20Shallum%20son%20of%20Tikvah%2C%20son%20of%20Harhas%2C%20the%20keeper%20of%20the%20Temple%20wardrobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EShe%20said%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20has%20spoken!%20Go%20back%20and%20tell%20the%20man%20who%20sent%20you%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20I%20am%20going%20to%20bring%20disaster%20on%20this%20city%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E22%3A16%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethis%20place%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2022%3A19%2C%2020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20its%20people.%20All%20the%20words%20written%20in%20the%20scroll%20that%20the%20king%20of%20Judah%20has%20read%20will%20come%20true.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20my%20people%20have%20abandoned%20me%20and%20offered%20sacrifices%20to%20pagan%20gods%2C%20and%20I%20am%20very%20angry%20with%20them%20for%20everything%20they%20have%20done.%20My%20anger%20will%20burn%20against%20this%20place%2C%20and%20it%20will%20not%20be%20quenched.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20go%20to%20the%20king%20of%20Judah%20who%20sent%20you%20to%20seek%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20tell%20him%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20says%20concerning%20the%20message%20you%20have%20just%20heard%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_19%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20were%20sorry%20and%20humbled%20yourself%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20when%20you%20heard%20what%20I%20said%20against%20this%20city%20and%20its%20people%26%23x2014%3Bthat%20this%20land%20would%20be%20cursed%20and%20become%20desolate.%20You%20tore%20your%20clothing%20in%20despair%20and%20wept%20before%20me%20in%20repentance.%20And%20I%20have%20indeed%20heard%20you%2C%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_22_20%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2222%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20will%20not%20send%20the%20promised%20disaster%20until%20after%20you%20have%20died%20and%20been%20buried%20in%20peace.%20You%20will%20not%20see%20the%20disaster%20I%20am%20going%20to%20bring%20on%20this%20city.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3ESo%20they%20took%20her%20message%20back%20to%20the%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_1%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Kings%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJosiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Religious%20Reforms%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20summoned%20all%20the%20elders%20of%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_2%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20king%20went%20up%20to%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20with%20all%20the%20people%20of%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem%2C%20along%20with%20the%20priests%20and%20the%20prophets%26%23x2014%3Ball%20the%20people%20from%20the%20least%20to%20the%20greatest.%20There%20the%20king%20read%20to%20them%20the%20entire%20Book%20of%20the%20Covenant%20that%20had%20been%20found%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20took%20his%20place%20of%20authority%20beside%20the%20pillar%20and%20renewed%20the%20covenant%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20presence.%20He%20pledged%20to%20obey%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20by%20keeping%20all%20his%20commands%2C%20laws%2C%20and%20decrees%20with%20all%20his%20heart%20and%20soul.%20In%20this%20way%2C%20he%20confirmed%20all%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20covenant%20that%20were%20written%20in%20the%20scroll%2C%20and%20all%20the%20people%20pledged%20themselves%20to%20the%20covenant.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20instructed%20Hilkiah%20the%20high%20priest%20and%20the%20priests%20of%20the%20second%20rank%20and%20the%20Temple%20gatekeepers%20to%20remove%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple%20all%20the%20articles%20that%20were%20used%20to%20worship%20Baal%2C%20Asherah%2C%20and%20all%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20heavens.%20The%20king%20had%20all%20these%20things%20burned%20outside%20Jerusalem%20on%20the%20terraces%20of%20the%20Kidron%20Valley%2C%20and%20he%20carried%20the%20ashes%20away%20to%20Bethel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20did%20away%20with%20the%20idolatrous%20priests%2C%20who%20had%20been%20appointed%20by%20the%20previous%20kings%20of%20Judah%2C%20for%20they%20had%20offered%20sacrifices%20at%20the%20pagan%20shrines%20throughout%20Judah%20and%20even%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Jerusalem.%20They%20had%20also%20offered%20sacrifices%20to%20Baal%2C%20and%20to%20the%20sun%2C%20the%20moon%2C%20the%20constellations%2C%20and%20to%20all%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20heavens.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20removed%20the%20Asherah%20pole%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple%20and%20took%20it%20outside%20Jerusalem%20to%20the%20Kidron%20Valley%2C%20where%20he%20burned%20it.%20Then%20he%20ground%20the%20ashes%20of%20the%20pole%20to%20dust%20and%20threw%20the%20dust%20over%20the%20graves%20of%20the%20people.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20also%20tore%20down%20the%20living%20quarters%20of%20the%20male%20and%20female%20shrine%20prostitutes%20that%20were%20inside%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20where%20the%20women%20wove%20coverings%20for%20the%20Asherah%20pole.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_23_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2223%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EJosiah%20brought%20to%20Jerusalem%20all%20the%20priests%20who%20were%20living%20in%20other%20towns%20of%20Judah.%20He%20also%20defiled%20the%20pagan%20shrines%2C%20where%20they%20had%20offered%20sacrifices%26%23x2014%3Ball%20the%20way%20from%20Geba%20to%20Beersheba.%20He%20destroyed%20the%20shrines%20at%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20gate%20of%20Joshua%2C%20the%20governor